name: Beef Stroganoff With Rice Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Heat oil in a pan and sear beef strips until brown. Set aside.
Into the pan add onion and mushrooms. Once soft, add back the beef strips and stir to combine.
Snip and pour MasterFoodsÂ® Beef Stroganoff recipe base and stir through. Simmer uncovered for 10 minutes.
Stir through light sour cream and simmer for 1 minute or until heated through.
Serve with rice (cooked as per instruction on pack) and garnish with continental parsley (optional).
